metadata.name: CYBA (1)
metadata.description: Data Entry 29-11 The Encounter: Strange transmission from deep space! They came out of nowhere. At first they seemed intrigued by us, sharing their technology with us and we with them. That's when it all changed. Once we no longer seemed to be of any use to them they began to show their true intentions. I hope this broadcast reaches you before they do. Beware they are not friendly, they want only one thing. Domination!
